WEBVTT

00:00:00.788 --> 00:00:04.584
I've been a television comedy writer
for almost 25 years.

00:00:04.584 --> 00:00:07.712
I have written sketches and animated shows

00:00:07.712 --> 00:00:08.880
and sitcoms,

00:00:08.921 --> 00:00:10.131
but for the last decade,

00:00:10.131 --> 00:00:13.134
my real passion has been
the study of ethics.

00:00:13.801 --> 00:00:16.345
It's a classic cautionary tale, right?

00:00:16.721 --> 00:00:17.889
You move to Hollywood,

00:00:17.930 --> 00:00:20.516
you get seduced by the bright lights
and the fast cars,

00:00:20.516 --> 00:00:21.726
and before you know it,

00:00:21.768 --> 00:00:23.853
you're reading 18-century
German philosophy.

00:00:23.853 --> 00:00:25.396
(Laughter)

00:00:25.772 --> 00:00:27.899
I've always been an intense rule follower.

